                    <thead>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Phase</entry>
                            <entry>Workshop</entry>
                            <entry>Advisory traject</entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Analysis</entry>
                            <entry namest="c2" nameend="newCol3">Identify current working
                                practices,goals, ambitions and limitations.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Planning</entry>
                            <entry>
                                <p>Align goals, ambitions and limitations.</p>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <p>Align goals, ambitions and limitations and define improvement
                                    tracks and alternatives.</p>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Execution</entry>
                            <entry>
                                <p>Conduct the workshop </p>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <p>Implementation of these improvement tracks supported with
                                    workshops and coaching.</p>
                                <p>Depending on the specific situation, interim management is a
                                    option.</p>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
